EPIQSS Overview

This is a website that provides support information, how to, and an reference for the API for EPIQSS

Application Information

  • Location: Contental US
  • Users: Internal WNCINC Employees
  • Purpose: To created, edit, and keep track of inspections on various WNCINC Properties
  • Platform: iOS (iPad ONLY)
  • Version Number:
  • Technologies: Swift

Features

  • Viewing Inspections
  • Editing Inspections
  • Generating Reports
